                    </div>
                    <span>I got this book as a prize at a Java User Group meeting. Overall, it's a good reference book to keep. One thing I wish it had covered is the JSPs, since it does cover the Servlets.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">great book !!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
